reviewText: Have not looked at it yet but I'm sure it is good.
This is not at all what I expected , it is not full of the Bible , word for word , but is a story about children in a school setting who sing hip hop gospel songs with a few Bible stories mixed in.
It is a Christmas gift,it did very well. The colors were great , truth is told, very well put to gether with video.

I used this for Children's ministry. The kids stayed interested though this as this is the story of Jesus through the eyes of children.
If it can keep the attention of 1st and 2nd graders, I think older children would enjoy.
Very good! Wasn't crazy about Jesus teaching with his shirt off, but the teaching is very accurate.  My kids loved it!
